data.title: Kelsey Grammer Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Kelsey Grammer on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Kelsey Grammer including Toy Story 2, X-Men: The Last Stand, and more.

Meanwhile, Philâs dad, Frank (Fred Willard) arrives with his new girlfriend, who happens to be Philâs childhood babysitter, which sets him on a confusing tailspin. Reaganing

Jack (Alec Baldwin) is having a perfect day and succeeding at every task. He tries to channel his winning streak into helping Liz (Tina Fey) figure out her relationship with Carol. Meanwhile, Jenna (Jane Krakowski) and Kenneth (Jack McBrayer) enlist the help of Kelsey Grammer (guest starring as himself) to pull off an ice cream scam. Elsewhere, Tracy (Tracy Morgan) is trying to shoot a commercial for the Boys and Girls Club. Also starring: Keith Powell, Judah Friedlander, Scott Adsit and Katrina Bowden.

Idiots Are People Two!

Drama erupts at TGS when a cell phone video leaks onto the web with Tracy Jordan (Tracy Morgan) on an offensive rant. Liz (Tina Fey) tries to do damage control. Meanwhile, Jackâs refusal to approve of Lizâs new boyfriend causes her to question the validity of her relationship. Kenneth (Jack McBrayer) and Jenna Maroney (Jane Krakowski) call on Kelsey Grammer when a problem arises that only the Best Friends Gang can handle.
